T02TD1249E:209b-1: shr'i he badzra s'a dha nam /
T02TD1249E:209b-3: dpal dgyes pa rdo rje'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD1249E:209b-4: dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1249E:209b-5: dpa' bo thod pa'i phreng ba can //
T02TD1249E:210a-0: @210a * // nam mkha' khyab par gar mdzad cing //
T02TD1249E:210a-1: bdag med ma dang gnyis med gzugs //
T02TD1249E:210a-2: bde chen de la phyag 'tshal bdud //
T02TD1249E:210a-3: de nyid rnyed dka' de bas kyang //
T02TD1249E:210a-4: bla ma'i bka' ston shin tu dka' //
T02TD1249E:210a-5: bdag gzhan don 'byung sngags kyi tshul //
T02TD1249E:210a-6: 'gro phan lam la brten par gyis //
T02TD1249E:210a-7: yon tan brgyad ldan sngags pa yis //
T02TD1249E:210a-8: bde ba'i stan la nyer 'dug ste //
T02TD1249E:210a-9: sems nyid rang gi snying gar bsam //
T02TD1249E:210a-10: 'od kyis bdag dang sems can sbyangs //
T02TD1249E:210a-11: de la chos 'byung yangs la blta //
T02TD1249E:210a-12: mi 'gyur ba nyid yongs gyur las //
T02TD1249E:210a-13: dpal ldan rdo rje he ru ka ;
T02TD1249E:210a-14: / zhal gcig phyag gnyis nag po che //
T02TD1249E:210a-15: gar gyi zhabs kyis nyi ma mnan //
T02TD1249E:210a-16: phyag rgya drug gis brgyan pa ste //
T02TD1249E:210a-17: rdo rje thod pa g-yas g-yon 'chang //
T02TD1249E:210a-18: gri gug thod pa 'dzin pa yi //
T02TD1249E:210a-19: bdag med ma yis mgul nas 'khyud //
T02TD1249E:210a-20: spyan gsum dbu sgra gyen du 'bar //
T02TD1249E:210a-21: bde bas gang ba'i rang bzhin du //
T02TD1249E:210a-22: bdag nyid rnam par bsgom par bya //
T02TD1249E:210a-23: snying gar ye shes sems dpa' yi //
T02TD1249E:210a-24: 'od kyis grub pa'i lha bkug ste //
T02TD1249E:210a-25: mchod pa la sogs byas pa'i mthar //
T02TD1249E:210a-26: bdag dang gnyis su med par bsam //
T02TD1249E:210a-27: de nas dbang bskur byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1249E:210a-28: yang na mchod pas mnyes bya ste //
T02TD1249E:210a-29: dbang po gnyis kyis sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1249E:210a-30: dang po sangs rgyas mchod par bya //
T02TD1249E:210a-31: bde chen dam pa de blangs nas //
T02TD1249E:210a-32: lte ba'i rtsa bar ngal bso te //
T02TD1249E:210a-33: bdud rtsi btung bar bya ba nyid //
T02TD1249E:210a-34: de yi lus ni rnam dag 'byung //
T02TD1249E:210a-36: bde bar gshegs pa lnga bsregs te //
T02TD1249E:210a-37: spyan la sogs pa yang bsregs te //
T02TD1249E:210a-38: bsregs pa ham las ri bong 'dzag / thog ma tha ma dbus med cing //
T02TD1249E:210a-40: bdag dang gzhan yang yod min pa //
T02TD1249E:210a-41: 'od ni mchog tu bde chen po //
T02TD1249E:210a-42: de lta bu dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1249E:210a-43: dang po nyid du bden pa'i byin rlabs brjod de /
T02TD1249E:210a-44: gnas dang yul du rgyu ba'o //
T02TD1249E:210a-45: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma rnams kyis bdag la byin gyis rlobs shig ces brjod la /
T02TD1249E:210a-47: ye shes 'od ni shin tu zab //
T02TD1249E:210a-48: rdo rje snying po mkha' dang mtshungs //
T02TD1249E:210b-0: rdul bral mthar ster @210b zhi ba ste //
T02TD1249E:210b-1: nga yi pha ni nga nyid do //
T02TD1249E:210b-2: 'dir ni rigs skyes dam tshig ldan //
T02TD1249E:210b-3: rjes su chags par dgyes rdor 'chang //
T02TD1249E:210b-4: bla ma la gus snying rje can //
T02TD1249E:210b-5: skye zhing skye bar bdag gyur cig / lag pa rdo rje dril bu 'khrol //
T02TD1249E:210b-7: btsun mo'i khu bas mnyam zas can //
T02TD1249E:210b-8: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog / de nas gtor ma btang nas su //
T02TD1249E:210b-9: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab //
T02TD1249E:210b-10: bde bar gshegs pa'i sngags bzlas shing //
T02TD1249E:210b-11: lha yi sbyor bas rgyu bar bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-12: rtag tu slob ma bsdu bya zhing //
T02TD1249E:210b-13: rtag tu dam chos bshad par bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-14: sems can thams cad rtag tu bskyang //
T02TD1249E:210b-15: he ru ka dpal rtag tu mchod //
T02TD1249E:210b-16: s'a tsha sbyin sreg mchod sbyin bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-17: chu sbyin rang gi sbyin pas bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-18: bla ma bde gshegs mdun bdar te //
T02TD1249E:210b-19: mandala byi dor byas nas su //
T02TD1249E:210b-20: mchod cing bstod de gshegs gsol bgyi //
T02TD1249E:210b-21: gling bzhi nyi ma re re bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-22: de bzhin thun mtshams gzhan la yang //
T02TD1249E:210b-23: bdag la byin gyis brlab par bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-24: skyil krung bcas nas dmigs brtan te //
T02TD1249E:210b-25: sna rtser bsams pa mi g-yo bas //
T02TD1249E:210b-26: brel kyang skad cig skabs bshol la //
T02TD1249E:210b-27: khyim pa yis kyang bsgom par bya //
T02TD1249E:210b-28: spyod lam dag la bab na yang //
T02TD1249E:210b-29: sgyu ma rmi lam lta bur bsgom //
T02TD1249E:210b-30: lhan cig skyes pa'i yid kyis nyal //
T02TD1249E:210b-31: sems can don la chags pas ldang //
T02TD1249E:210b-32: glo bur nyid du dran bya zhing //
T02TD1249E:210b-33: glo bur tshul du rnal 'byor spyod //
T02TD1249E:210b-34: mkha' la rgyu ba'i bya bzhin du //
T02TD1249E:210b-35: sngags pas chags pa med par gnas //
T02TD1249E:210b-36: gzhan du g-yeng bas chags sems dang //
T02TD1249E:210b-37: gnyid kyi zil gnon ma gyur cig / sgrub pa'i thabs 'di rin po che //
T02TD1249E:210b-38: rnal 'byor ba yang skal ba bzang //
T02TD1249E:210b-39: bzang po nga yis mdor bsdus pas //
T02TD1249E:210b-40: dge can gang yin rol par shog / dpal he ru ka zhal gcig pa'i sgrub thabs slob dpon yan lag med pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1249E:210b-42: // / rgya gar gyis mkhan po badzra p'a ni dang /
T02TD1249E:210b-43: bod kyi lo ts'a ba rma ban chos 'bar gyis bsgyur ba'o//
